  "description": "<p>在Build 2013大会上微软放出了自去年十月份Windows 8系统发布以来最大的系统更新Windows 8.1，在本次更新中最大的亮点在于开始按钮终于回归，此外搜索等细节特性也进行了强化改善。<strong>在本月的Patch Tuesday上微软再次通过Windows Update进行了更新。本次共为Windows 8放出了7个安全补丁，同样也为Windows 8.1推出了相关的安全更新。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e6ff18c/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244098.htm&amp;t=Patch+Tuesday%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E6%8E%A8Windows+8.1%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244098.htm&amp;t=Patch+Tuesday%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E6%8E%A8Windows+8.1%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244098.htm&amp;t=Patch+Tuesday%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E6%8E%A8Windows+8.1%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244098.htm&amp;t=Patch+Tuesday%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E6%8E%A8Windows+8.1%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244098.htm&amp;t=Patch+Tuesday%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E6%8E%A8Windows+8.1%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E